      "source": "Physics derivation",
      "topology": "flyback",
      "problem_statement": "Design a flyback converter for PoE (Power over Ethernet): Vin=48V, Vout=5V, Pout=15W, fsw=200kHz. Use turns ratio 4:1.",
      "specs": {
